DEPENDENCIES
	OpenGL    <http://opengl.org>
	SDL       <http://libsdl.org>
	SDL_ttf   <http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_ttf/>
	SDL_image <http://www.libsdl.org/projects/SDL_image/>

On OS X, SDL, SDL_ttf, and SDL_image MUST be compiled and installed manually.
They won't link correctly if you have them installed as frameworks. OpenGL is
installed by default on Macs.


INSTALLATION

	$ make
	$ make install

The default installation directory is /usr. To install to a custom location,
set the DESTDIR environment variable:

	$ make DESTDIR=/path/to/game
	$ make DESTDIR=/path/to/game install
